## How to use this playbook
- Treat the **ship-gates** as a pre-release checklist for every project.
- When implementing auth, DB access, storage, billing, or onboarding, re-read the
  matching section first.
- Keep it current: when the user teaches a new lesson (or a new video drops),
  append a dated note and commit. Don't let it drift.

